diff --git a/doc/whatsnew/fragments/9879.false_positive b/doc/whatsnew/fragments/9879.false_positive
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..2630563858
--- /dev/null
+++ b/doc/whatsnew/fragments/9879.false_positive
@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@
+Fix ``used-before-assignment`` false positive for names bound in only some arms of an ``if/elif/else`` chain.
+
+Closes #9879
